        "p_1": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Paperlux Studio is an interdisciplinary design studio based in Hamburg – since 2006, we’ve been creating brands, products and experiences that last.</p>"
          }
        },
        "p_2": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In 2020, they took over a long-standing bookbinding studio they had previously worked with as clients. Today, it is fully integrated into their practice – where prototypes, dummies and bespoke productions are realized with exceptional precision. This is also where their own Paperlux Studio collections like the One Word A Day series is produced.</p>"
          }
        },
        "p_3": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Paperlux is a studio, a lab and a place to think. Where analog craftsmanship meets digital precision – and design becomes more than visual: it becomes spatial, tactile, and memorable.</p>"
          }
        },
